text: Paraclathurella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Clathurellidae.MolluscaBase (2018). Paraclathurella Boettger, 1895. Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at: http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=432525 on 2018-02-22 ==Species== Species within the genus Paraclathurella include: * Paraclathurella aditicola Hedley, 1922 * Paraclathurella clothonis Hedley, 1922 * Paraclathurella densegranosa (Thiele, 1925) * Paraclathurella gracilenta (Reeve, 1843) * Paraclathurella padangensis (Thiele, 1925) * Paraclathurella thecla (Thiele, 1925) ==References== ==External links== * Bouchet, P.; Kantor, Y.
